Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.46,0:24:16.57,Main03,Shinpachi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.57,0:24:18.77,Main03,Shinpachi,0000,0000,0000,,Gonna be king of the Santas? It's March!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.77,0:24:20.58,Main03,Shinpachi,0000,0000,0000,,We're still doing these\NChristmas episodes?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.58,0:24:22.05,Main03,Gintoki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so anal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.05,0:24:24.71,Main03,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Keep talking like that and Santa\Nwon't visit your home this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.71,0:24:25.31,Main03,Shinpachi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.31,0:24:26.68,Main03,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And so, the next episode...
